OL,3,CThames Water to discover if
OL,4,Crestructuring plan has been approved
OL,6,FThames Water will discover whether a
OL,7,FHigh Court judge has approved plans to
OL,8,Frestructure the struggling utility on
OL,9,FTuesday (18 February).
OL,11,FThames Water Utilities Holdings
OL,12,FLimited (TWUH), the parent company of
OL,13,FThames Water Group (TWG), England's
OL,14,Flargest water company, is set to run
OL,15,Fout of money by late March and risks
OL,16,Fentering special administration if a
OL,17,Fjudge does not approve the scheme,
OL,18,Fknown as the company plan, to inject
OL,19,Fup to #3 billion to keep it afloat.
