OL,3,CThames Water to discover if
OL,4,Crestructuring plan has been approved
OL,6,FBut a smaller secondary group of
OL,7,Fcreditors opposes the sanctioning of
OL,8,Fthe plan and is instead proposing an
OL,9,Falternative known as the 'B plan'
OL,10,Fwhich it claims would provide the
OL,11,Fcompany with the same funding on
OL,12,Fbetter terms.
OL,14,FEarlier this month, Mr Justice Leech
OL,15,Fheard five days of arguments between
OL,16,Flawyers for TWUH and different groups
OL,17,Fof creditors over whether the company
OL,18,Fplan should be sanctioned.
