OL,3,CThames Water to discover if
OL,4,Crestructuring plan has been approved
OL,6,FThe judge is now expected to hand down
OL,7,Fjudgment at 9.30am on Tuesday, which
OL,8,Fwill be followed by a hearing dealing
OL,9,Fwith consequential matters arising
OL,10,Ffrom the ruling.
OL,12,FTWG serves about 16 million customers,
OL,13,Fabout 25% of the UK's population, and
OL,14,Fowns more than 20,000 miles of water
OL,15,Fmains and more than 68,000 miles of
OL,16,Fsewers across the Thames Valley,
OL,17,FLondon and the Home Counties.
OL,19,FIt has approximately 8,000 employees
OL,20,Fand more than 400 water and sewage
OL,21,Ftreatment sites.
