OL,3,CThames Water to discover if
OL,4,Crestructuring plan has been approved
OL,6,FBut the company is in about #16
OL,7,Fbillion of debt and needs #3.3 billion
OL,8,Fover the next five years to keep
OL,9,Frunning.
OL,11,FThe restructuring bid marks an attempt
OL,12,Fto shore up its finances without a
OL,13,Fbailout from investors.
OL,15,FIt has also been at the centre of
OL,16,Fgrowing public outrage over the extent
OL,17,Fof pollution, rising bills, high
OL,18,Fdividends, and executive pay and
OL,19,Fbonuses at the UK's privatised water
OL,20,Ffirms.
