OL,3,CThames Water to discover if
OL,4,Crestructuring plan has been approved
OL,6,FThe company plan would provide #1.5
OL,7,Fbillion of funding, with a further
OL,8,F#1.5 billion potentially available and
OL,9,Fa 9.75% interest rate.
OL,11,FIt has been approved by creditors
OL,12,Fholding more than 75% of its Class A
OL,13,Fdebt, which is worth about #11.5
OL,14,Fbillion and is the least risky class
OL,15,Fof bonds in its debt pile.
OL,17,FTom Smith KC, for the company, has
OL,18,Fpreviously said the plan was "an
OL,19,Finterim measure" to keep the company
OL,20,Frunning before a "substantive
OL,21,Frestructuring" due later this year.
