OL,3,CThames Water to discover if
OL,4,Crestructuring plan has been approved
OL,6,FThe utility's Class B bondholders drew
OL,7,Fup their rival scheme in October,
OL,8,Fwhich they say provides "committed"
OL,9,Ffunding of #3 billion with a lower
OL,10,Finterest rate of 8% and other
OL,11,Fdifferent terms.
OL,13,FThey have previously claimed that one
OL,14,Fterm of the company plan known as the
OL,15,FJune release condition, which concerns
OL,16,Fthe release of further funding, "holds
OL,17,Fthe company to ransom", and that the
OL,18,Fcompany's proposal leaves them worse
OL,19,Foff, meaning it cannot be approved.
